The member representing Ughelli North, Ughelli South and Udu Federal Constituency, Ejiroghene Francis Waive says the All Progressives Congress, APC has been in government but not in power in the past six years. The Federal lawmaker made the assertion during a consultative visit to the leader of the All Progressives Congress, APC in Ughelli South Local Government Area of Delta State, Ogbarode Napoleon Ogbon. He said till date, some members of the Peoples Democratic Party, PDP were still serving in over four hundred and fifty Federal boards in the country. Cross River: Gov Ayade sacks another Commissioner
